# Task 2 – SPPU Grade Calculator

-> Description
This is a Java-based ccode that calculates Grade Points, CGPA, and Percentage according to SPPU rules.

The user enters marks for 11 subjects, and the system:
- Converts marks into Grade Points (Out of 10)
- Displays subject-wise grade and pointer
- Calculates CGPA
- Calculates percentage
- Checks fail condition (marks < 40)

-> Features
- Subject-wise grade point calculation
- Automatic fail detection
- CGPA calculation
- Percentage calculation using SPPU formula
- Input validation (0–100 marks)

-> Technologies Used
- Java
- Arrays
- Loops
- Conditional statements


